						<summary>

						<p>This inscription of the reign of the Chālukya king <hi rend="bold">Kīrtivarma-Satyāśraya</hi> registers the gift of some land. The date of the record is lost. On palaeographic grounds the inscription may be assigned to the riegn of <hi rend="bold">Kīrttivarman II.</hi></p>						

						<p>First Face.</p>						

						</summary>
